8 Statement of purpose of bill as introduced: This bill proposes to require the
9 Agency of Education to develop a framework for considerations a school
10 district is required to make when considering merging with another district, as
11 well as require the Agency to provide advice on each consideration, including
12 cultural considerations when the districts considering merger have different
13 course offerings; how the community will navigate the cultural, social, and
14 identity implications of closing a school; how a district will help prepare
15 students for the transition if a school closes; how to help students through the
16 transition when they are attending school in a new building; how to repurpose
17 a school building after closure, including how to account for maintenance
18 costs; and how to factor in geographic proximity and transportation
19 considerations. This bill also proposes to create funding sources to assist with
20 the repurposing of closed school buildings; for facilitation around cultural
21 differences; and to support municipalities or districts that close a school
